            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:10:43",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "金地商置4 月合約銷售跌逾54%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金地商置(00535)公布，2025年4月的合約銷售總額約8.53億元(人民幣‧下同)，較去年同期18.55億元大跌54.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內合約銷售總面積約64100平方米，較去年同期16萬平方米跌59.94%，銷售均價為每平方米約13300元，較去年同期11600元升14.66%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首4月期間的累計合約銷售總額約32.52億元，按年跌41.85%，累計銷售總面積約245400平方米，按年跌42.16%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14913300-%e9%87%91%e5%9c%b0%e5%95%86%e7%bd%ae4-%e6%9c%88%e5%90%88%e7%b4%84%e9%8a%b7%e5%94%ae%e8%b7%8c%e9%80%be54",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250106_FI_source-web_00535-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-05-08 17:10:46",
